{"title":"Bikepacking Roots Community Routes: The Tobacco Root Gravel Loop","link":"https://theradavist.com/bikepacking-roots-community-routes-the-tobacco-root-gravel-loop/","date":1718201159000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2052\" height=\"1368\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_02.jpeg?fit=1200,1368&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_02.jpeg?w=2052&amp;quality=75 2052w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_02.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_02.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_02.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_02.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_02.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://bikepackingroots.org/project/tobacco-root-gravel-loop/\" target=\"_blank\">The Tobacco Root Gravel Loop</a>, created and stewarded by John Babcock and featuring some of southwestern <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bikepacking-little-belt-mountains-montana-bike-touring/\" target=\"_blank\">Montana’s big sky gravel roads</a>. This long weekender, 150-mile route circumnavigates the Tobacco Root Mountains.⁠..</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_01.jpeg?fit=1200,1366&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_01.jpeg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_01.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_01.jpeg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_01.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_01.jpeg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><br />\n⁠<br />\nThe route comes with burly climbs and thrilling descents suitable for a gravel bike. Featuring three hot springs, abandoned mines, a number of historic barns, plenty of scenic vistas, some refreshing rivers, and fan favorite friendly towns, this route is sure to touch all of the senses.⁠</p>\n<p>Check out the new route page and get some inspiration for your bucket list at <a href=\"https://bikepackingroots.org/project/tobacco-root-gravel-loop/\" target=\"_blank\">Bikepacking Roots</a>.</p>\n<p>⁠<img width=\"2042\" height=\"1362\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_03.jpeg?fit=1200,1362&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_03.jpeg?w=2042&amp;quality=75 2042w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_03.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_03.jpeg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_03.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BPR_CROP_03.jpeg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>This is the latest route to be shared as a part of the Community Routes Project!⁠ Follow along as BPR publish more routes throughout the year. If you have created or are working on a route that you think might be a good fit for this project, find out more information at <a href=\"https://bikepackingroots.org/ride/#community-routes\" target=\"_blank\">Bikepacking Roots</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bikepacking-roots-community-routes-the-tobacco-root-gravel-loop/\">Bikepacking Roots Community Routes: The Tobacco Root Gravel Loop</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"49a52cdd376b1b028187f79c4073b7f3ae054410889f3e90f96e2a117bb0abd8","category":"Cycling"}